id=zygisk-virtualizer
name=Universal Syscall Virtualization Framework
version=v1.0.0
versionCode=1
author=droid-re-chain
description=Global system call cloaking sandbox using SECCOMP_RET_USER_NOTIF to virtualize sensitive environment paths across all applications. Intercepts openat/readlinkat/faccessat natively and autonomously blocks root/magisk/anti-cheat path detection without ptrace overhead.
